hopobject.body: What's the last date I can post this to to arrive in time for Christmas? nisar pharmacy Yet the June data from the Realtors raises the question of whether rising rates are now already beginning to have the opposite effect, a question that remains unanswered until more time and data collection have elapsed. What we do know is the number of mortgage applications declined a seasonally adjusted 2.6% over the week ending July 12, after falling 4% in the seven days prior.
